            <title><![CDATA[#吃蛋黄会导致胆固醇升高吗# 【#体检发现血脂高怎么办#？为了健康，转存了解！】医生介绍：①体检报告中，高密度脂蛋白胆固醇升高不是坏事，若是低密度脂蛋白胆...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%90%83%E8%9B%8B%E9%BB%84%E4%BC%9A%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E8%83%86%E5%9B%BA%E9%86%87%E5%8D%87%E9%AB%98%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%90%83%E8%9B%8B%E9%BB%84%E4%BC%9A%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E8%83%86%E5%9B%BA%E9%86%87%E5%8D%87%E9%AB%98%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#吃蛋黄会导致胆固醇升高吗#</span></a> 【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%BD%93%E6%A3%80%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E8%A1%80%E8%84%82%E9%AB%98%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%8A%9E%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%BD%93%E6%A3%80%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E8%A1%80%E8%84%82%E9%AB%98%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%8A%9E%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#体检发现血脂高怎么办#</span></a>？为了健康，转存了解！】医生介绍：①体检报告中，高密度脂蛋白胆固醇升高不是坏事，若是低密度脂蛋白胆固醇、总胆固醇或甘油三酯升高，可能需要干预。②高胆固醇更多与遗传因素、日常生活方式有关，正常吃蛋黄对体内胆固醇影响不大。③体检发现血脂高要控制饮食、增加锻炼，对胆固醇过高的中老年人建议遵医嘱药物治疗。一起关注<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[开学季]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/72/2021_kaixueji_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4951297208811548" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a> <a href="https://weibo.com/n/%E5%A4%AE%E8%A7%86%E6%96%B0%E9%97%BB">@央视新闻</a> <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hiddrb2s7rj60l60s81cs02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/FQdyKORBlx088YOrFFUA01041200pg0q0